msgid ""
"The categorical fixed effect '%s' must have fewer levels than the overall "
"number of observations."
msgstr "類別固定效果「%s」的層級數必須少於總觀察值數。"

msgid ""
"The random effects grouping factor '%s' must have fewer levels than the "
"overall number of observations."
msgstr "隨機效果分組因子「%s」的層級數必須少於總觀察值數。"

msgid ""
"The number of iterations must be at least 2 iterations higher than the burnin"
msgstr "疊代次數必須比預燒期至少多 2 次疊代"

msgid "%s requires that the dependent variable is positive."
msgstr "%s 要求依變數為正值。"

msgid "%s requires that the dependent variable is an integer."
msgstr "%s 要求依變數為整數。"

msgid "%s requires that the dependent variable contains only two levels."
msgstr "%s 要求依變數僅包含兩個層級。"

msgid "%s requires that the number of trials variable is an integer."
msgstr "%s 要求試驗次數變數為整數。"

msgid ""
"%s requires that the number of successes is lower that the number of trials."
msgstr "%s 要求成功次數低於試驗次數。"

msgid ""
"%s requires that the dependent variable is higher than 0 and lower than 1."
msgstr "%s 要求依變數大於 0 且小於 1。"

msgid ""
"%s requires that the dependent variable is either the number or proportion "
"of successes out of the number of trials."
msgstr "%s 要求依變數為成功次數或試驗次數中的成功比例。"

msgid ""
"At least one random effect needs to be specified for the '%1$s' random "
"effect grouping factors.%2$s"
msgstr "至少需要為「%1$s」隨機效果分組因子指定一個隨機效果。%2$s"

msgid ""
"Parametric bootstrap is not supported for %s family. Please use a different "
"test method (e.g., likelihood ratio test)."
msgstr "參數拔靴法不支援 %s 分佈族。請使用其他檢定方法（例如概似比檢定）。"

msgid ""
"Mixed-effects models with a fixed intercept only are not supported for "
"aggregated binomial family."
msgstr "僅包含固定截距的混合效果模型不支援聚合二項式分佈族。"

