msgstr "抽樣診斷"

msgid "Avg. autocorrelation"
msgstr "平均自我相關"

msgid ""
"The following variables are a linear combination of each other, please, "
"remove one of them from the analysis: %s"
msgstr "下列變數彼此存在線性組合關係，請從分析中移除其中一個：%s"

msgid ""
"The intercept corresponds to the (unweighted) grand mean; for each factor "
"with k levels, k - 1 parameters are estimated with sum contrast coding. "
"Consequently, the estimates cannot be directly mapped to factor levels. Use "
"estimated marginal means for obtaining estimates for each factor level/"
"design cell or their differences."
msgstr ""
"截距對應於（未加權）總平均數；對於具有 k 個層級的每個因子，使用總和對比編碼估"
"計 k - 1 個參數。因此，估計值無法直接對應到因子層級。請使用估計邊際平均數來獲"
"取每個因子層級／設計單元的估計值或其差異。"

msgid ""
"The intercept corresponds to the mean in the default factor category (factor "
"level parameters are estimated with treatment contrast coding). "
"Consequently, the estimates cannot be easily interepreted in the presence of "
"interactions. Use estimated marginal means for obtaining estimates for each "
"factor level/design cell or their differences."
msgstr ""
"截距對應於預設因子類別的平均數（因子層級參數使用處理對比編碼估計）。因此，在"
"存在交互作用的情況下，估計值不易解讀。請使用估計邊際平均數來獲取每個因子層級"
"／設計單元的估計值或其差異。"

msgid ""
"The intercept corresponds to the (unweighted) grand mean; for each factor "
"with k levels, k - 1 parameters are estimated with orthonormal coding "
"proposed by Rouder et al. (2012). Consequently, the estimates cannot be "
"directly mapped to factor levels. Use estimated marginal means for obtaining "
"estimates for each factor level/design cell or their differences."
msgstr ""
"截距對應於（未加權）總平均數；對於具有 k 個層級的每個因子，使用 Rouder 等人 "
"(2012) 提出的正交編碼估計 k - 1 個參數。因此，估計值無法直接對應到因子層級。"
"請使用估計邊際平均數來獲取每個因子層級／設計單元的估計值或其差異。"

msgid ""
"Model fit is singular. Specified random effects parameters (random "
"intercepts and random slopes) cannot be estimated from the available data. "
"Carefully reduce the random effects structure, but this practice might "
"inflate the reported p-value, and invalidates the analysis."
msgstr ""
"模型擬合為奇異。無法從現有資料中估計指定的隨機效果參數（隨機截距與隨機斜率）"
"。請謹慎簡化隨機效果結構，但此做法可能會使報告的 p 值膨脹，並使分析失效。"

msgid ""
"Vovk-Sellke Maximum <em>p</em>-Ratio: Based on a two-sided <em>p</em>-value, "
"the maximum possible odds in favor of H%1$s over H%2$s equals 1/(-e <em>p</"
"em> log(<em>p</em>)) for <em>p</em> %3$s .37 (Sellke, Bayarri, & Berger, "
"2001)."
msgstr ""
"根據 Sellke、Bayarri 和 Berger（2001）的研究，Vovk-Sellke 最大<em>p</em>-比率"
"是基於雙尾<em>p</em>-值而計算的，在<em>p</em> %3$s .37的情況下，假設 H%1$s 相"
"對於 H%2$s 的最大勝算比為：1/(-e <em>p</em> log(<em>p</em>))。"

msgid ""
"Numerical problems with the maximum-likelihood estimate (e.g., gradients too "
"large). This may indicate that the specified random effects parameters "
"(random intercepts and random slopes) cannot be estimated from the available "
"data. Consider carefully reducing the random effects structure, but be aware "
"this may induce unknown risks of anti-conservative results (i.e., p-values "
"might be lower than nominal)."
msgstr ""
"最大概似估計出現數值問題（例如梯度過大）。這可能表示所指定的隨機效應參數（隨"
"機截距與隨機斜率）無法從現有資料中估計。建議仔細考慮簡化隨機效應結構，但需注"
"意這可能導致反保守結果的未知風險（即 p 值可能低於標稱值）。"

msgid ""
"Estimation of degrees of freedom disabled (i.e., asymptotic results shown), "
"because the number of observations is large. To force estimation, check "
"corresponding option."
msgstr ""
"自由度估計已停用（即顯示漸近結果），因為觀察值數量過大。如需強制估計，請勾選"
"對應選項。"

msgid "Results are on the response scale."
msgstr "結果以反應尺度呈現。"

msgid "Results are not on the response scale and might be misleading."
msgstr "結果未以反應尺度呈現，可能會產生誤導。"

msgid "Type %s Sum of Squares"
msgstr "型 %s 平方和"

msgid ""
"This analysis requires at least one random effects grouping factor to run."
msgstr "此分析至少需要一個隨機效應分組因子才能執行。"

msgid ""
"The 'Binomial (aggregated)' family requires the 'Number of trials' to be "
"specified to run."
msgstr "「二項式（聚合）」族別需要指定「試驗次數」才能執行。"

msgid "P-values correspond to test of null hypothesis against %s."
msgstr "P 值對應於針對 %s 的虛無假設檢定。"

msgid "Results are averaged over the levels of: %s."
msgstr "結果已對以下層級取平均：%s"

