msgid ""
"Inference possibly unreliable -- MCMC chains might not have converged; R-hat "
"cannot be computed for all parameters due too few distinct samples. Please "
"re-scale the variables or increase 'Iterations', or 'Adapt delta' in the "
"Options section."
msgstr ""
"推論可能不可靠——MCMC 鏈可能未收斂；由於有效樣本數過少，無法計算所有參數的 R-"
"hat。請重新縮放變數，或在選項區塊中增加「疊代次數」或「Adapt delta」。"

msgid ""
"Inference possibly unreliable -- MCMC chains might not have converged; The "
"largest R-hat is %.3f > 1.01. To lower R-hat please increase 'Iterations', "
"or 'Adapt delta' in the Options section."
msgstr ""
"推論可能不可靠——MCMC 鏈可能未收斂；最大 R-hat 為 %.3f > 1.01。若要降低 R-hat"
"，請在選項區塊中增加「疊代次數」或「Adapt delta」。"

msgid ""
"Inference possibly unreliable -- MCMC chains might not have converged; "
"Effective Sample Size (ESS) cannot be computed for all parameters due too "
"few distinct samples. Please re-scale the variables or increase "
"'Iterations', or 'Adapt delta' in the Options section."
msgstr ""
"推論可能不可靠——MCMC 鏈可能未收斂；由於有效樣本數過少，無法計算所有參數的有效"
"樣本數 (ESS)。請重新縮放變數，或在選項區塊中增加「疊代次數」或「Adapt delta」"
"。"

msgid ""
"Low estimation accuracy -- The smallest Effective Sample Size (ESS) is "
"%1$.2f < %2$1.0f. To increase accuracy please increase 'Iterations', or "
"'Adapt delta' in the Options section."
msgstr ""
"估計準確度低——最小有效樣本數 (ESS) 為 %1$.2f < %2$1.0f。若要提高準確度，請在"
"選項區塊中增加「疊代次數」或「Adapt delta」。"

msgid ""
"The model was fitted using restricted maximum likelihood. Please note that "
"models with different fixed effects cannot be compared when REML is used. To "
"use ML, switch 'Test method' to 'Likelihood ratio tests'."
msgstr ""
"此模型使用限制性最大概似法 (REML) 進行擬合。請注意，使用 REML 時無法比較具有"
"不同固定效果的模型。若要使用 ML，請將「檢定方法」切換為「概似比檢定」。"

msgid "The model was fitted using maximum likelihood."
msgstr "此模型使用最大概似法進行擬合。"

msgid ""
"The optimizer failed to find a solution. Probably due to quasi-separation in "
"the data. Try removing some of the predictors."
msgstr "最佳化器未能找到解。可能由於資料中存在準完全分離。請嘗試移除部分預測變數。"

msgid ""
"The optimizer failed to find a solution. Probably due to quasi-separation in "
"the data or an overly complex model structure. Try removing some of the "
"predictors."
msgstr ""
"最佳化器未能找到解。可能由於資料中存在準完全分離或模型結構過於複雜。請嘗試移"
"除部分預測變數。"

msgid ""
"The optimizer failed to find a solution due to invalid starting values. "
"(JASP currently does not support specifying different starting values.)"
msgstr "由於起始值無效，最佳化器未能找到解。（JASP 目前不支援指定不同的起始值。）"

msgid ""
"The optimizer failed to find a solution. Probably due to scaling issues "
"quasi-separation in the data. Try rescaling or removing some of the "
"predictors."
msgstr ""
"最佳化器未能找到解。可能由於資料中存在縮放問題或準完全分離。請嘗試重新縮放或"
"移除部分預測變數。"

msgid ""
"The optimizer failed to find a solution in the specified number of "
"iterations. (JASP currently does not support modifying the optimizer "
"settings.)"
msgstr "最佳化器在指定的疊代次數內未能找到解。（JASP 目前不支援修改最佳化器設定。）"

msgid "The model formula is probably too long. Try shortening variable names."
msgstr "模型公式可能過長。請嘗試縮短變數名稱。"

msgid ""
"The Kenward-Roger degrees of freedom approximation failed because the "
"variance-covariance matrix is singular. This can happen with overly complex "
"models or when the model structure does not support this method. Try using "
"asymptotic degrees of freedom instead."
msgstr ""
"Kenward-Roger 自由度近似失敗，原因是變異數-共變數矩陣為奇異矩陣。這可能發生於"
"模型過於複雜或模型結構不支持此方法。建議改用漸近自由度。"

msgid "The following variable is used as a random effects grouping factor: %s."
msgid_plural ""
"The following variables are used as random effects grouping factors: %s."
msgstr[0] "以下變數被用作隨機效應分組因子：%s."

msgid ""
"All random slopes involving ‘%1$s’ have been removed for the random effects "
"grouping factor ‘%2$s’. -- Factor %3$s does not vary within the levels of "
"random effects grouping factor '%4$s'."
msgid_plural ""
"All random slopes involving ‘%1$s’ have been removed for the random effects "
"grouping factor ‘%2$s’. -- Factors %3$s do not vary within the levels of "
"random effects grouping factor '%4$s'."
msgstr[0] ""
"隨機效應分組因子「%2$s」中，所有涉及「%1$s」的隨機斜率已被移除 —— 因子 %3$s "
"在隨機效應分組因子「%4$s」的層級內沒有變異。"

msgid ""
"Random slope of ‘%1$s’ for the random effects grouping factor ‘%2$s’ removed "
"-- Too few observations to estimate random slope of '%3$s' for random "
"effects grouping factor '%4$s'."
msgid_plural ""
"Random slopes of ‘%1$s’ for the random effects grouping factor ‘%2$s’ "
"removed -- Too few observations to estimate random slopes of '%3$s' for "
"random effects grouping factor '%4$s'."
msgstr[0] ""
"隨機效應分組因子「%2$s」中「%1$s」的隨機斜率已移除 —— 觀察值過少，無法估計隨"
"機效應分組因子「%4$s」中「%3$s」的隨機斜率。"

msgid ""
"Lower order random effects terms need to be specified in presence of the "
"higher order random effects terms. Therefore, the following random effects "
"term was added to the '%1$s' random effects grouping factor: '%2$s.'"
msgid_plural ""
"Lower order random effects terms need to be specified in presence of the "
"higher order random effects terms. Therefore, the following random effects "
"terms were added to the '%1$s' random effects grouping factor: '%2$s.'"
msgstr[0] ""
"在存在高階隨機效應項時，需要指定低階隨機效應項。因此，已將以下隨機效應項加入"
"隨機效應分組因子「%1$s」：'%2$s'"

msgid "%i observation was removed due to missing values."
msgid_plural "%i observations were removed due to missing values."
msgstr[0] "因缺失值，已移除 %i 筆觀察資料。"

msgid ""
"The Hamiltonian Monte Carlo procedure might be invalid -- There was %i "
"divergent transition after warmup. This can be solved by carefully "
"increasing 'Adapt delta' until there are no divergent transitions."
msgid_plural ""
"The Hamiltonian Monte Carlo procedure might be invalid -- There were %i "
"divergent transitions after warmup. This can be solved by carefully "
"increasing 'Adapt delta' until there are no divergent transitions."
msgstr[0] ""
"Hamiltonian Monte Carlo 程序可能無效 —— 熱身後出現 %i 次發散轉換。可透過逐步"
"增加「Adapt delta」直到不再有發散轉換來解決此問題。"

msgid ""
"Bayesian Fraction of Missing Information (BFMI) that was too low in %i chain "
"indicating that the posterior distribution was not explored efficiently. Try "
"increasing number of 'Burnin' and 'Iterations'."
msgid_plural ""
"Bayesian Fraction of Missing Information (BFMI) that was too low in %i "
"chains indicating that the posterior distribution was not explored "
"efficiently. Try increasing number of 'Burnin' and 'Iterations'."
msgstr[0] ""
"貝葉斯缺失資訊比例（BFMI）在 %i 條鏈中過低，表示後驗分布未被有效探索。可嘗試"
"增加「Burnin」與「Iterations」次數。"

msgid ""
"The Hamiltonian Monte Carlo procedure might be inefficient -- %i transition "
"exceeded the maximum tree depth. This can be solved by carefully increasing "
"'Maximum tree depth'."
msgid_plural ""
"The Hamiltonian Monte Carlo procedure might be inefficient -- %i transitions "
"exceeded the maximum tree depth. This can be solved by carefully increasing "
"'Maximum tree depth'."
msgstr[0] ""
"Hamiltonian Monte Carlo 程序可能效率低下 —— %i 次轉換超過最大樹深度。可透過逐"
"步增加「Maximum tree depth」來解決此問題。"

msgid ""
"WAIC estimate unreliable -- There was %1.0f p_waic estimate larger than 0.4. "
"We recommend using LOO instead."
msgid_plural ""
"WAIC estimate unreliable -- There were %1.0f p_waic estimates larger than "
"0.4. We recommend using LOO instead."
msgstr[0] "WAIC 估計不可靠 —— 有 %1.0f 個 p_waic 估計值大於 0.4。建議改用 LOO。"

msgid ""
"LOO estimate unreliable -- There was %1.0f observation with the shape "
"parameter (k) of the generalized Pareto distribution higher than 0.5."
msgid_plural ""
"LOO estimate unreliable -- There were %1.0f observations with the shape "
"parameter (k) of the generalized Pareto distribution higher than 0.5."
msgstr[0] "LOO 估計不可靠 —— 有 %1.0f 筆觀察值的廣義帕累托分布形狀參數 (k) 大於 0.5。"
